2ï¸âƒ£ Slicing vs Splitting

Slicing: returns a view (shares memory)

Splitting: returns new arrays

Slicing is commonly used inside models

Splitting is used for dataset preparation and batching

3ï¸âƒ£ Stacking Arrays

np.vstack() â†’ adds rows (stack samples)

np.hstack() â†’ adds columns (stack features)

